# Oscillink: Self‚ÄëOptimizing Physics-Based Memory System

**Physics‚Äëbased coherence system that improves with use. Latency drops as your dataset grows. Hallucinations reduced. Every decision signed and deterministic.**



<p>
	<a href="https://github.com/Maverick0351a/Oscillink/actions/workflows/ci.yml"><img alt="CI" src="https://github.com/Maverick0351a/Oscillink/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg"/></a>
